        <p style="margin-bottom: var(--s-5); max-width: 760px;">A large share of our professional-services clients are mid-career &mdash; partner-track at a firm, buying a CPA practice, exiting BigLaw to hang their own shingle, acquiring a competitor&rsquo;s book of business. The personal mortgage isn&rsquo;t the only loan in the file; SBA acquisition financing, capital-call notes, and seller-financing schedules all interact with your personal qualification. We sequence and structure the personal mortgage to fit the practice transaction, not the other way around.</p>
